  "text": "Our task was more complex than the task used in the study discussed above [CITATION_1] : it did not imply the categorization of words into negative or positive, but instead required the partial reactivation of experience related to these words. This enabled us to reveal that experience within the domain of approach behaviour is less differentiated compared to experience within the domain of avoidance behaviour.",
